Pro Circuit Monster Brigade Backpack
content:
백팩 사이즈: 가로 30cmX 세로 15cmX 높이 50cm
백팩 무게: 997g

Perfect for holding school supplies, your laptop or even an extra set of clothing
Embroidered team logos and bold graphics make this backpack an item to have over your shoulder
Armor-protected dedicated laptop compartment fits most 15” laptops
Deluxe organization panel with zippered stash pocket
Dual side water-bottle/accessory holders
Fully adjustable ergonomic shoulder straps with sternum strap
Increased shoulder strap foam padding creates sweet spot comfort zone
Integrated foam panels keep your electronics and other valuables protected
Padded iPad/tablet/e-reader pocket
Quick-access expandable phone pocket
Soft-touch padded neoprene grab handle
Zippered, fleece-lined valuables pocket
Backpack measures 20” H x 12” W x 6” D; weighs 2.2 lb.

name: Pro Circuit Monster Rig Roller Bag
content:
모든 장비를 한번에 수납할수 있도록 디자인 되었습니다.
모든지형에 부드럽게 이동할수 있도록 강하고 큰 휠로 제작되었습니다.
메인 포켓에는 여러 구획으로 나눌수 있으며, 헬멧보관 하는곳에는 충격흡수가 되도록 패드처리 되었습니다.
크기 : 높이 86cm X 가로 42cm X 세로 38.7cm
기본 무게 : 6.44Kg
용량 : 160리터

Carry your gear in style with this feature-packed deluxe roller bag
Embroidered team logos and graphics make it stand out in a crowd
SLED (Structural Load Equalizing Deck) System ensures smooth handling on any surface
Large main compartment with adjustable dividers and padded helmet chamber
Easy-access small compartments for secure storage
iFOM (integrated foam) construction protects your gear
Heavy duty oversized wheels, compression strap system and telescoping handle make it easy to take wherever you go
34” H x 16.5” W x 15.25” D, weighs 14.2 lb. 9,792 cubic inch capacity

name: Pro Circuit Monster Trunk Roller Bag
content:
큰 사이즈의 휠을 장착하여 어떤 지형에서든지 부드럽게 움직입니다.
메인 포켓은 통풍이 잘되도록 제작되었습니다.
U자 모양의 큰 지퍼로 큰 부피의 라이딩기어를 넣고 빼기가 쉽습니다.
크기 : 가로 80cm X 세로 44.5cm X 높이 38cm

Heavy duty chassis with oversized treaded wheels
Wide Mouth U-Shaped opening for easy access to all gear
Large main ventilated compartment and multi-use dual end pockets
Secondary end pocket with accessory organization sleeves for smaller gear
iFOM integrated foam panel construction through out for added gear protection
Telescoping pull handle and padded adjustable shoulder strap
Easy grab end handles for transport
Dimensions: 31.5" H x 15" W x 17.75" D
9150 cubic inche capacity
